| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0128 — Recovery Inhibition (cloak)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78e5bd6c-ecb2-5d81-bb3d-72c1060350b2"
